    "slug": "is-curbnturf-free-membership-myths",
    "title": "Is CurbNTurf Free? Debunking Membership Myths for RV Travelers",
    "category": "boondocking",
    "categoryLabel": "Boondocking",
    "author": "Dustin Reed",
    "publishedAt": "2026-04-21",
